                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18271206-139-off724 t18271206-139-cd725"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 2d.; 2 half-crowns, 2 shillings, and 1 sixpence, the property of 
                     <persName id="t18271206-139-victim800" type="victimName">
                        Elizabeth 
